Class DefinitionToSparkVisitor

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cerner.bunsen.spark.converters.DefinitionToSparkVisitor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DefinitionVisitor<HapiConverter<org.apache.spark.sql.types.DataType>>

    public class DefinitionToSparkVisitor
extends Object
implements DefinitionVisitor<HapiConverter<org.apache.spark.sql.types.DataType>>
    A visitor implementation to travers a FHIR resource definition and produce a converter class that translates from FHIR to Spark and vice versa.

        Creates a visitor to construct Spark Row conversion objects.
        Parameters:
        fhirSupport - support for FHIR conversions.
        basePackage - the base package to be used as a prefix for unique keys to cache generated converters.
        visitedConverters - a mutable cache of generated converters that may be reused by types that contain them.
